Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The next step is to rewire the cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t watch television that close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren’t you playing with the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know how to play anything that they’re playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You’re from outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so you’re not familiar with our grassland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your task today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is to cultivate the grassland’s interest into BB Goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cultivate interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Soccer is certainly the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Gardening is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think working out is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I can focus fully
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,on my experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I capture BB Goat this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With this shapeshifting potion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can transform into anything I touch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can transform back whenever I want to, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can also use it to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, how about I play with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I want to fly kites!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I want to play with a teddy bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s play, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought Wolffy would have an actually useful invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I drink this potion, it’s game over for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the ball go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is soccer, BB Goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so dizzy…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now’s my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Overhead kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s odd. How did it get over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let BB Goat touch the ball, Weslie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I got lost in the moment there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got kicked around for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you pick up the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not kicking the ball. It’ll hurt the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess BB Goat doesn’t like playing soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s try something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s see if you can kick me around now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how to use punching bags, BB Goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that’s too much force!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you have something normal to show her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat will for sure like the things that I do all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping neither harms the body nor consumes energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s perfect for goats who don’t like moving, such as BB Goat and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn’t even count as exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I’ll give you guys a taste
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of my ultimate move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess BB Goat doesn’t like what you guys have to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that I’ll succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if I try just a little harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those goats are way too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d better just hide and wait for a chance to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your house is so organized, Tibbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A chance has come faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,why don’t I teach you how to water plants?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Watering plants? That’s all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no skill in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Watering plants requires a lot of precision, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t give too much or too little water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t be too rough with your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The flower is dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right now, Sister Tibbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen such a condition before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have messed up just a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but you’ve done a great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it’s my turn next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to get in trouble sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I’m this small, I won’t be—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we run out of yarn,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we can tie multiple strands together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t washed my feet in some days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This sock isn’t quite breathable enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you like, BB Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the sock can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the sock is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly how long have you not washed your feet for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ours is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ours is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ours is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ours is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat should take after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She should take after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,870)}Us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}She should take after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s ask BB Goat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat, who do you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I play with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! BB Goat is on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Skateboarding is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exhausting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The skateboard walks and talks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that’s King Bacteria’s voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don’t, I’ll jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let BB Goat go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever met a king that just lets go when you ask him to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No one shall stop me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job minding your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I recover my powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take over the whole universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Recall the strongest sleeping position that I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My super strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thermofist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Wolffy’s inventions are awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Knitters are very good at making knots, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t spill when watering plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it precise and elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Overhead kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you guys argued over this for a whole day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, BB Goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to play with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, what BB Goat wanted is to just play with us.
